{"tid":2335734,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人大常委會公布反食品浪費法草案　禁暴飲暴食節目","createTime":"2020-12-22T05:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T06:13:08.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eb1c1f5fc3cbab8795dbc0fe39f94aed9c35a49f","tid":2335734,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:48:36.000Z","msg":"今次人大常委會會議一連五日在北京舉行，暫時公布的議程沒有涉及香港的事項，會二審國防法修訂草案，又首次公開反食品浪費法草案，列明禁止電視台、網站等製作、發布、傳播宣揚暴飲暴食等浪費食物節目，最高可罰十萬元人民幣；又訂明餐廳可向浪費食物的顧客收取處理廚餘費用，並禁止餐廳誘導顧客過量點菜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=417516\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417516&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2Ff3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=29b72e71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417516&h=d6cd2983\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=417516</a>"},{"pid":"99b05b8a5d23a96e4a620d63f928394906fdb388","tid":2335734,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:50:11.000Z","msg":"蛇齋餅粽新年<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7b7ead756bc9655b0cf0f4397727b2202595f6","tid":2335734,"uid":122601,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T06:05:26.000Z","msg":"當 人民自己細路仔咁管教 好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又唔比打機 又唔比食野 遲d強制埋溫書呀"},{"pid":"af4e3e169aa669a221a1cca78de6de3743857c0b","tid":2335734,"uid":375135,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eb1c1f5fc3cbab8795dbc0fe39f94aed9c35a49f","tid":2335734,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:48:36.000Z","msg":"今次人大常委會會議一連五日在北京舉行，暫時公布的議程沒有涉及香港的事項，會二審國防法修訂草案，又首次公開反食品浪